Steps to login in G5K
----------------------------------------------------
1. ssh account@access.grid5000.fr
2. Connect to a selected site, such as luxmbourg
3. Run the orchestration.sh to reserv nodes and to deploy OS and Ethereurm blockchain
4. Run the mining.sh to make nodes gain some Ether for experiments 
5. Use the stop.sh to kill geth clients in all nodes
6. Use console-only.sh to run the geth client in all nodes
